content: Yiwen Xu is a second year postgraduate student in the School of Computer Science and Engineering, UNSW. He has great enthusiasm for computer vision and deep learning; accordingly, he studied a lot of related courses during his postgraduate studies and gain some [course certificate](‘#accomplishments’).
